{"tid":1875431,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"搞一次民間公投，組成真港人政府無得諗？","createTime":"2020-02-11T19:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T18:09:30.000Z","uid":125434,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7b416585a871b48ffcec8933e9df49b371d15416","tid":1875431,"uid":125434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T19:14:00.000Z","msg":"我知道成件事好長遠，但用民間公投向國際展示香港政府嘅應受性低作為第一步，及後自組港人政府促請各國承認呢個方向有冇得諗？"},{"pid":"c32423d1331a6773038d5b1b70914aca30e85ec9","tid":1875431,"uid":179715,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T19:20:38.000Z","msg":"依加根本係成立臨時政府最好時機<br />\n利申講緊法國大革命"},{"pid":"35ec7e2a59916573d8b28ce3ebd0bf8d16def4fe","tid":1875431,"uid":323132,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T21:32:02.000Z","msg":"呢個係最基本同最正確做法 但由上年六月講到而家d人都唔做 其實簡單係各區嘅社區中心或區議員辦事處度開始搞就可以"},{"pid":"997304a6b9c991439975d989b86f166ad136402b","tid":1875431,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c32423d1331a6773038d5b1b70914aca30e85ec9","tid":1875431,"uid":179715,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T19:20:38.000Z","msg":"依加根本係成立臨時政府最好時機<br />\n利申講緊法國大革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T01:01:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/republicofhongkong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Frepublicofhongkong%2F&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2Bcpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=919b5e89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/republicofhongkong/</a>"},{"pid":"ad0bf1efdb930ada981e4022f4d525f6f09641ca","tid":1875431,"uid":125434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T01:56:45.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhhh"},{"pid":"e24a5f02f3fdf00e1783a0462589380b60d4e776","tid":1875431,"uid":125434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma